# GEMS
# Gem (package) regarding the theme in use: "just-the-docs"
# Fixed version: "0.4.0.rc3" -> this is due to hardcoding being used. WARNING: modifying the version below requires to manually update all the hardcoded files (each hardcoded file will signalated inside the file itself)
# Defining HARDCODING: using manually written / pasted code from a specific version that won't be updated automatically when the theme's repo is updated: not updating these files but still using a newer vesrion of the theme may cause errors.
